text: Rosalba consobrina is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Melzer in 1934. It is known from Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Rosalba consobrina. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1934
title: Rosalba consobrina
